Medicare Temporal Endpoint

Source: R/S7_care.R
careTemp.Rd

Medicare Temporal Endpoint

Usage

careTemp(alias)

Arguments

alias

<chr> title alias

Value

An S7 <careTemp> object.

Examples

careTemp("quality_payment")
